  <entry>
    <title>你好成都</title>
    <link href="http://weekdaycare.cn/posts/chengdu/"/>
    <id>http://weekdaycare.cn/posts/chengdu/</id>
    <published>2023-05-08T04:57:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-05-09T11:08:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="tag-plugin note" color="red"><div class="body"><p>多图预警！！！</p></div></div><p>五一七天小长假，简直堪比国庆！为什么有七天捏？酱酱！因为我们有运动会，而且运动会刚好是在五一前面滴（26、27号），周五又只有一节体育课，相当于没有，这么连起来一算，喔嚯嚯，好家伙，七天小长假到手！这么好的假期不出去玩一玩着实是有些可惜了。话虽然是这么说，但是嘛，大家都是这么想的，结果就emm……到处都是人挤人，以及，票是真的难抢！</p><p>25号下午出发，捎点秦黄酥，踏上去往成都的火车。不得不说，这才25号啊！还没到五一呢，西安的人就已经开始多起来了，着实是恐怖！（听我舍友说他五一出去过一次之后就再也不想出去了，西安城墙上面的想下去下面的想上来，围城是吧）</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459e4369b986.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459e52097c46.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459e55c3704a.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459e56f8a411.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459e583b91e3.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459e608a132c.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><p>道友们听我一句劝，出去玩一定一定别选晚上的硬座了，太遭罪了！晚上九点上的火车，第二天早上八点钟到，十一个小时！你知道这十一个小时我是怎么过来的吗！他不熄灯！我醉了，我本来以为他晚上好歹会熄灯的，结果是我想多了😭。他的灯亮了一晚上，我根本没法睡，我尝试过眯一会儿，但是吧，那个硬座根本不可能会让你有稍微好一点的姿势。最崩溃的是，西安到成都这段，都是山洞！然后就失联了……没网！只恨没有事先准备几部电影呐😭。然后吧，车上就……就挺冷的🥶，冷风一阵一阵地吹，吹了我一晚上。所以，从第二天早上开始就感冒了……到现在也没好🥺。道友们不要学我，出门前要做好攻略，不要像我一样傻乎乎的就出门了🤡。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459e8df34406.webp" alt="早上终于到了" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">早上终于到了</span></div></div><p>出站了第一件事那肯定是要好好补偿一下我的肚子！循着香味走去，直接在路边摊开炫！</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459ea9678ec9.webp" alt="好次，就是分量有点少，几口就没了" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">好次，就是分量有点少，几口就没了</span></div></div><p>炫完了有劲儿了，去哪儿？</p><p>去学校！😭</p><p>别人的旅途是换个地方吃沙县小吃，我的旅途是换个地方继续坐牢🤡</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459ebe1bed14.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><p>其孜楼？孜然楼！别笑我哈哈，我舍友第一眼也是孜然楼😋果然在吃货眼里啥都是吃的。</p><p>虽然是坐牢，但是！不管怎么样不能亏待了自己的肚子。大晚上十二点才吃的烤鱼🤣</p><div class="tag-plugin gallery swiper" id="swiper-api" effect="coverflow"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459eeaa68652.webp" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459eec998503.webp" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459eeda6525c.webp" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459eee578cc3.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div><div class="swiper-button-prev blur"></div><div class="swiper-button-next blur"></div></div><p>坐牢坐完了，那就出去走走吧！</p><h2 id="锦里">锦里</h2><p>这鸟地方人是真的多，看什么？看后脑勺！所以让我疑惑的是，为啥有家店叫厕所串串？这老板是有啥恶趣味儿嘛。</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459f2cb40475.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459f355e05a6.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459f38c6c5f5.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459f400d8e6a.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459fe6e12e05.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459fe9faad32.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><p>美食出列！只是吧，这里的小吃看起来一般，吃起来嘛，也一般……而且基本上每一个都是15的定价。就拿我吃的那个炸豆腐来说吧，味道是真的不行（可能是我吃的那家店不行）他那个炸豆腐真的就是豆腐的味道，酱汁是一点没有沁入进去，我本以为他的炸豆腐是两面煎至焦黄呢，看来是我想得美了。看着好吃结果第一口我就不想再吃了。还不如我小时候吃的铁板豆腐呢！这个豆沙千丝饼倒是有点紧实，就是吧，分量挺小，以及得配水喝哈哈。</p><div class="tag-plugin gallery swiper" id="swiper-api" effect="coverflow"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459febebc103.webp" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/6459fee86140a.webp" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a016165a4b.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div><div class="swiper-button-prev blur"></div><div class="swiper-button-next blur"></div></div><h2 id="青龙湖">青龙湖</h2><p>公园之大，宛若一朵盛开在城市中心的奇葩花朵，既美丽、又壮观，让人惊艳不已。走在这片美丽的土地上，仿佛是在与大自然亲密接触，感受到了它的美好与神秘。在广阔无垠的土地上，数不尽的人们搭起帐篷，展开露营之旅，令我无限敬佩。他们是如何在无数蚊虫的猛烈袭扰中坚守自己的领地，不为所动，仍能享受自然风光的美妙呢？小孩们手牵风筝，飞舞于天空之间，令人心旷神怡。人群涌动，热闹非凡，仿佛构成了一幅生动的画卷，令人心生向往。</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a07d74abf4.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a07f731bfc.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a080e4e833.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a0828b6c88.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a084c92f7b.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><p>突生的体力不支搅乱了原本构建脚步回响图，心灵再怎么斗志昂扬也难以抵挡肚子的咕咕作响。无奈之下，只得放弃原定计划，掉头返回，略感遗憾。</p><h2 id="宽窄巷子">宽窄巷子</h2><p>坦白地说，我并未感受到宽窄巷子和锦里之间有什么明显的区别。一样的人山人海，一样的川剧，一样的美食。相较于初次见到时的惊艳，如今在人群中挤动已经开始显得有些乏味。毕竟，熟悉的景象再怎么美丽，也会随着时间的推移而逐渐失去新鲜感。（只走了宽巷子，窄巷子嘛，你们懂的，挤不进去……）</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a128c3f1cd.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a128b0b869.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a128732c04.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1288ca3d5.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1285eb35b.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1284be032.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a128281edc.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1283a0412.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><h2 id="人民公园">人民公园</h2><p>吃完晚饭，顺路来到人民公园。早已耳闻公园里的人们喜欢在此喝茶、看戏，而今儿个才算是第一次见了。往里捎捎，倒显得有些阴森，夜幕下五彩缤纷的灯光散发出诡异而神秘的气息。</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a140dbc652.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a14401a9f5.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a144d9353c.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a145d083cd.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a16d12d6a3.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a16dea8d17.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a16f08a29c.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a16fb7b530.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a170a01805.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><p>吐槽下我的手机，大晚上拍的和个白天一样，一点氛围感都没了。</p><h2 id="锦门">锦门</h2><p>你们见过地上的地铁吗？我算是真的见过一次了。坐上地铁我真有种感觉我不是在坐地铁，而是在坐轻轨。踏入锦门，仿佛穿越回到了民国时期，连垃圾桶都变得典雅起来，不禁让我感到有些格格不入。</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1aa4d84d4.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1b03c065e.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1a6291abb.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1a718999e.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1a81a3a54.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a22915c218.jpeg" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><h2 id="建设路">建设路</h2><p>说到吃的，建设路肯定不能少。一条gai的吃的，就是这个队嘛，得排老远了。路上听到两个人说：给我五千我都不敢在这里随便吃（笑</p><p>实际上咱也没有吃建设路的，而是去了建设路周围的一家馄饨店试了试，味道不戳嘿嘿，就是这生煎包吧太迷你了。</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1da04d14b.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1db1c4d8b.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1dc40f373.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1dce49a56.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><p>快乐的时光总是短暂的，转眼间七天已经过去了。虽然感觉没有玩够，但是陪伴女友的时光却让我倍感珍贵。那下次就选个不那么坐牢的时间再来好好玩一下吧！（对了地铁人是真的多，站一个小时真的受不了</p><p><pwd>最后，老样子女朋友镇楼！</pwd></p><div class="tag-plugin gallery swiper" id="swiper-api" effect="coverflow"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a1fc37abc8.webp" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="swiper-slide"><img no-lazy src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/05/09/645a21aac99ce.jpeg" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div><div class="swiper-button-prev blur"></div><div class="swiper-button-next blur"></div></div>]]></content>
    
    
