  <entry>
    <title>千年古都，常来长安</title>
    <link href="http://weekdaycare.cn/posts/changan/"/>
    <id>http://weekdaycare.cn/posts/changan/</id>
    <published>2023-03-13T11:42:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-03-13T12:42:23.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言">前言</h2><p>咕咕咕，我就是鸽子我不装了。这么长时间没更新主要是在<del>搞开学考</del>懒。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/13/640f3945a4d6b.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:200px;"/></div></div><p>现在考完了就有时间出去玩一玩啦。作为一个在陕读的大学牲，没去长安玩几次实属是丢脸。好不容易挺过了疫情，现在终于可以出去逛逛咯。</p><h2 id="第一站钟楼">第一站：钟楼</h2><p>虽说是周末，但是实际上也没有多少时间能够逛完所有的景点，西安的景点挺分散的。所以我们决定逛逛一些比较著名的景点，那作为交通枢纽的钟楼，自然是第一站啦哈哈。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/640f49185b1a8.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:800px;"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/13/640f438dd029a.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:800px;"/></div></div><p>没了白日的宏伟，夜与光交相辉映，映衬出钟楼辉煌庄严的影子。剥落的城墙，又诉说着历经的沧桑。</p><p>可惜的是夜晚的钟楼并不开放，无法驻足眺望远方。</p><h2 id="第二站回民街">第二站：回民街</h2><p>刚步入大学之时有幸去过一次回民街，只可惜由于疫情原因都没有开放。而今日有幸窥得其全貌，然光顾着吃，忘却了拍照。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/640f4b997726d.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:800px;"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/640f4a80e4ac4.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:800px;"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/640f4cd726420.webp" alt="叫啥忘了" fancybox="true" style="width:300px;"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">叫啥忘了</span></div></div><h2 id="第三站早市">第三站：早市</h2><p>熙熙攘攘的人群，匆忙的脚步弥散着“赶集”的气息。五颜六色的人，过着五颜六色的生活，穿过五颜六色的街道，吃着同一份早点。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/640f4e473c109.webp" alt="勿幕门" fancybox="true" style="width:800px;"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">勿幕门</span></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/640f54072f5fd.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:400px;"/></div></div><h2 id="第四站西安城墙">第四站：西安城墙</h2><p>白日的城墙倒是少了一些神秘感，看不到城墙上的日落也算是一个小小的遗憾。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/64100188e35c7.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:800px;"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641002c8b1d61.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641003a0dc4c1.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/6410074dc0b32.webp" alt="曾经晚上上过的一次城墙" fancybox="true" style="width:700px;"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">曾经晚上上过的一次城墙</span></div></div><p>只可惜的是城墙实在是太长了，我们甚至没能走完1/8，城墙上也有租自行车的，好像挺贵的。</p><h2 id="第五站长安十二时辰">第五站：长安十二时辰</h2><p>本来是想去芙蓉园的，结果下起了雨，还夹杂着沙尘暴。不得不吐槽一下西安的空气质量，下的雨都夹着黄沙，打到我白色的衣服上一下子就黄了，实在是太可恶了。</p><div class="tag-plugin quot"><p class="content" type="text">祷以恒切，盼以喜乐，苦以坚忍，必有所得。</p></div><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/6410626adf6b4.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/64106900aae46.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/64106957e21cb.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641065a70a01b.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/64106324b4217.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/64106932a7678.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641069816eb9a.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641067fd9a978.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><h2 id="第六站大唐不夜城">第六站：大唐不夜城</h2><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/15/64109d6729a92.webp" fancybox="true" style="width:300px;"/></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/15/64109e28dad63.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><p>不夜城倒是挺有意思的，路两旁都是小摊，里面是各式各样的吃的。不过一直和女朋友牵着手，没顾着拍照欸嘿。</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/15/6410a3b71efc3.webp" alt="唐食坊" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">唐食坊</span></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/15/6410a436b215d.webp" alt="步行街" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">步行街</span></div></div></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/15/6410a1d565231.webp" alt="你甚至能听听民谣演唱会" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">你甚至能听听民谣演唱会</span></div></div><h2 id="第七站老菜场">第七站：老菜场</h2><p>依偎在城墙脚下，乍看像是还在装修的样子，实际上确实是在装修哈哈哈<span class="tag-plugin emoji"><img no-lazy="" class="inline" src="https://raw.weekdaycare.cn/raw/waline-blobcatemojis/main/blobs/ablobcatrainbow.png"/></span></p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/64108ea986417.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><p>开个小玩笑，没怎么去逛过里面，所以只在外沿逛了逛。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/6410900ecee95.webp" alt="老默也没鱼吃" fancybox="true"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">老默也没鱼吃</span></div></div><p>上过几层阶梯，来至天台</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641090cdb426d.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><p>放眼望去，昔日的城墙，今日却被高耸的建筑压下了气焰。格格不入的身影，又略显落魄凄凉。</p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/6410912f91406.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/6410952c8071c.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641094616aed5.webp" alt="where are you?" fancybox="true" style="width:400px;"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">where are you?</span></div></div><p>这里啊，我不得不点名批评一下楼上一家叫树岛 treeisland 的店了。</p><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/14/641095c5bb608.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div><p>右边那杯是我点的，叫做<mark class="tag-plugin mark" color="orange">秘密花园</mark>，菜单上没有任何关于它的描述，<strong>38一杯</strong>。你说它贵就算了，味道还贼拉奇妙。入口有点点冰红茶的味道，随后跟着一股中药味，你说它是咖啡吧，它也没有咖啡味儿，你说它不是咖啡吧，它又比咖啡还醒脑。我有一瞬间都在怀疑我不是在喝饮品，而是在喝什么稀奇古怪的药。总之，避雷！</p><h2 id="end">End</h2><p>时间很短暂，两天的时间并不够逛完西安的全部景点，所以只去了这一些啦。总的来说，西安确实是一座古代气息浓厚的城市，但又正是因为其古代气息，导致其在<strong>某些地方</strong>无法与现代很好的接轨，突兀的景点搭上突兀的建筑，只有一种说不上来的违和感。西安的城市治理也并不是很好，就拿我逛过的回民街来说，就没见着几个垃圾桶，基本都是一堆垃圾摊在地上，让人十分无语，早晚高峰的地铁也是堵的水泄不通。虽然说西安有着这样那样的缺点，但它绝对值你来逛一逛（最好是晚上）。不为别的，单纯的感受一下古都的气息与魅力，站在古与今的交界处，恍惚，回首，几千年悄然流逝，宫阙万将都做了土，只剩斑驳的城墙在风中飘零。</p><p>最后，女朋友镇楼！<psw>我女朋友真好看！</psw></p><div class="tag-plugin grid" ><div class="cell" index="0"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/15/64109ed22d312.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div><div class="cell" index="1"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/03/15/64109f2dbc375.webp" fancybox="true"/></div></div></div></div>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">不装了，我就是来晒女朋友的</summary>
    
    
    
